11 TOWNS OF BAILEY AND WEAVERVILLE/CITY OF CHERRYVILLE SATELLITE
12 ANNEXATION CAP REMOVAL
13 SECTION 1. G.S. 160A-58.1(b) reads as rewritten:
14 "(b) A noncontiguous area proposed for annexation must meet all of the following
15 standards:
16 …
17 (5) The area within the proposed satellite corporate limits, when added to the area
18 within all other satellite corporate limits, may not exceed ten percent (10%)
19 of the area within the primary corporate limits of the annexing city.
20 This subdivision does not apply to the Cities of Archdale, Asheboro,
21 Belmont, Cherryville, Claremont, Concord, Conover, Durham, Elizabeth
22 City, Gastonia, Greenville, Hickory, Kannapolis, Kings Mountain, Locust,
