12 The portion of Parcel No. 3536159662 lying north of Dollard Town Road (State Road No.
13 1727), being approximately 1 acre and more particularly described in the deed to Diamond
14 Poultry Farms, Inc. (now Sleepy Creek Farms, Inc.), dated November 7, 1961, and recorded in
15 Deed Book 559, Page 134, of the Wayne County Registry.
16 PARCEL B:
17 Parcel No. 3536267029, including the right-of-way of Dollard Town Road (State Road No.
